  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, F</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, creating a dormant seal that can be activated as an instant action to grant you a +2 competence bonus to Defense against a single attack, a single attack roll or a single Reflex save. The seal can be activated only if it's bonus would be used immediately, before the result of the roll is known, and disappears afterwards. You take 2 damage every time you attempt to perform this technique. Your body cannot carry more than one Celerity seal.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend double the Chakra and double the damage dealt to you to double the bonuses granted. Doing so makes you unable to use this technique or Ketsuyoujutsu: Seiryoku for 24 hours.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
